ji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似係話帶佢去睇睇器材<br />\n之後就簽咗份嘢<br />\n就話係上咗堂<br />\n所以冇得退<br />\n（中心個邊話個堂兩點開始<br />\n我朋友2點後上去簽嘢<br />\n都話佢上咗兩點個堂）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知佢戇鳩+佢問題<br />\n唔想咁直接咁講..."},{"pid":"b0269c9eecfb3e22d6cbdc6286026dfd8267cf2e","tid":190661,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>心甘情願俾錢 個呃位喺邊？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉，佢頭先講唔清楚<br />\n我以為又呃又逼個啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我錯.."},{"pid":"2a1eadf02c6f3e37877b70e15aff0c43e2249baa","tid":190661,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:12:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真<br />\n攞齊所有收據，合約<br />\n去海關，消委會睇下幫唔幫到你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢得收據<br />\n係咪唔多掂？"},{"pid":"71921202f4aed640a5448421d9aea3c4212c1329","tid":190661,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:14:51.000Z","msg":"叫咗佢去報消委會同搵議員<br />\n仲有咩可以做？"},{"pid":"8039d8a5cec9205a6f36dd337051b9c3a5ed37ea","tid":190661,"uid":71441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:17:38.000Z","msg":"佢地就係對我個frd，係沙田physical用呢招狗，避過冷静期呢條例。<br />\n我上左去兩次，係啲客面前瘋狂大聲屌佢三小時。講到明我唔會停，屌到你報警，一齊去落口供為止，成功退款。"},{"pid":"89e0c76f86c3ae0a527c24c1e370f48585fa867d","tid":190661,"uid":39508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:33:42.000Z","msg":"早叫你搵胡師父喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde21e8960f4c8f57841139fcec56a9c3be9df6c","tid":190661,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地就係對我個frd，係沙田physical用呢招狗，避過冷静期呢條例。<br />\n我上左去兩次，係啲客面前瘋狂大聲屌佢三小時。講到明我唔會停，屌到你報警，一齊去落口供為止，成功退款。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 